		color: #475569;
		line-height: 1.8;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
	}

	/* Hide inactive content */
	.top-mu-cus-content {
		display: none;
		animation: fadeInTab 0.3s ease-in-out;
	}

	.top-mu-cus-content.active {
		display: block;
	}

